{
  "texts": [
    "Common Objectives and Outcomes of STEM TPD.",
    "The synthesis of the analyzed studies highlights a collaborative endeavour within China's educational system to improve teachers' STEM competencies through PD.",
    "An important goal in different regions, ranging from busy cities such as Beijing to provinces such as Hunan, is to enhance teachers' capacity to incorporate STEM subjects into unified learning experiences (Liu et al. 2014; Lyu et al. 2022; Zheng et al. 2023).",
    "Several studies emphasize the importance of interdisciplinary integration and curriculum reform to address the evolving demands of STEM education.",
    "For instance, Jian et al. (2023) and Li and Li (2023) highlight that revising the pre-service training curriculum and integrating STEAM principles can significantly improve teachers' problem-solving skills and foster a more integrated approach to teaching."
  ]
}